WEBVTT

00:06:59.213 --> 00:07:02.714
One of the most off-putting
things you can say is,

00:07:02.738 --> 00:07:04.300
"Just get over it."

00:07:05.411 --> 00:07:07.380
Great idea -- love it,

00:07:07.404 --> 00:07:09.721
it's just we already thought of that.

00:07:09.745 --> 00:07:16.154
(Laughter)

00:07:16.178 --> 00:07:20.455
The absence of the ability
to just get over it is depression.

00:07:20.479 --> 00:07:24.292
(Laughter)

00:07:24.316 --> 00:07:29.162
(Applause)

00:07:29.186 --> 00:07:32.925
We feel it in our bodies --